19/06/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- EU Ambassador Lutz Salzmann expressed optimism Wednesday (18 June) about Albania's chances for integration into the Union. 
Despite problems confronting local authorities, the country is steadily on its way, Salzmann said. 
He pointed to the decision to open talks on EU accession as a concrete step in that direction. 
(ATA, BBC - 18/06/03)
